{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens of badge"}]},{"type":"text","text":" for "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"badge","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" objects like ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSBadge"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllBadgeComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"text":" so as to provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"text":" implementation to use.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBadgeComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"It implements also the protocol ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"BadgeComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"badge"}]},{"text":" through any ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Badge"}]},{"text":" components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of dime